    public class CheckQualityReadTransformer
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.broadinstitute.hellbender.transformers.ReadTransformer
    Checks for and errors out when it detects reads with base qualities that are not encoded with phred-scaled quality scores, each RTDefaults.SAMPLING_QUALITY_CHECKING_FREQUENCY. Note: this is adapted from the GATK3 not back-ported behaviour of MisencodedBaseQualityReadTransformer.
